answers.answer: Happened to me from July to August. It really stinks to have to repeat weeks!!
*****. But, I bet I will wind up delivering two weeks early as I did with my other two because of preeclampsia. Go figure!

question: Thanks guys for having me, but my OB/GYN bumped my due date back by two weeks into September! Imagine that the 11th. How could it go back so far? A anyone have that happen to them? I wonder if the baby is measuring small or what. I bet I will still wind up delivering in August. Once I change the due date in the settings it will move me into the September group. Thanks for having me while I repeat another week.
title: EDD is bumped adios August group!
